title: Woman Feeding Baby Dark Skin Tone
alsoKnownAs: Dark skin tone woman feeding baby
description: Represents a mother with dark skin tone breastfeeding or bottle-feeding her baby. It signifies nurturing, care, and the bond between a mother and child.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the woman feeding baby (dark skin tone) emoji radiates warmth and tender care, depicted with Apple's signature smooth gradients and soft rounded edges. The mother's loving expression and the gentle posture of the child are captured with realistic lighting, emphasizing the intimate bond. This emoji beautifully represents nurturing, motherhood, and the universal act of feeding a child, presented with inclusive and heartfelt detail.
